{"tid":2184221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新澤西州少女發起遊行被追收警員加班費 事件曝光當局撤回帳單","createTime":"2020-09-01T11:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T11:49:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd8c2349bfd4c88b526942dea5fceb3c4c88b43","tid":2184221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200901/X6D4OCQCWZAJLP4REOZLSMGIOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200901%2FX6D4OCQCWZAJLP4REOZLSMGIOQ%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=608025c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200901%2FX6D4OCQCWZAJLP4REOZLSMGIOQ%2F&h=6a39d0dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200901/X6D4OCQCWZAJLP4REOZLSMGIOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n新澤西州一名18歲少女吉爾（Emily Gil），在七月底發起支持「黑人性命可貴」（Black Lives Matter， BLM）遊行，同時有感當地樓價高，批評州政府多年來，沒有政策協助低收入民眾置業。當遊行集會結束後，她收到一封來自當地市長發出的信件，要求集會發起人繳交2,500元（美元、下同）的警員加班費用。當地市長在事件曝光後，撤回相關帳單。"}]}